name: Rollin' (Air Raid Vehicle)
wikiSummary: According to the Rollin' (Air Raid Vehicle) Songfacts, this defiant middle finger to Limp Bizkit's detractors became the group's only #1 song in the UK, a position it maintained for three weeks.
